sequenceDiagram
    participant B as 买家
    participant FE as Vue 前端
    participant TC as TradeController
    participant TS as TradeService
    participant DB as Database
    participant MS as ConversationService
    participant NS as NotificationService
    participant S as 卖家

    B->>FE: 点击“我想要”
    FE->>TC: POST /api/items/{id}/reserve
    TC->>TS: reserve(userId, itemId)
    TS->>DB: 悲观写锁读取商品
    TS->>DB: 校验并更新商品状态=被预定
    TS->>DB: 创建 TradeOrder
    TS->>MS: 创建/复用私信会话
    TS->>NS: 创建系统通知
    TC-->>FE: orderId + conversationId
    FE-->>B: 跳转聊天页
    NS-->>S: 卖家在消息页看到通知
